@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
 
 @{b}HARDWARE REQUIREMENTS@{ub}

 - Amiga Computer with a minimum of 1 MB Ram

 @{b}NEEDED SOFTWARE@{ub}

 - Kickstart 2.0/Workbench 2.0 or higher
 - FAME Mainpart version v1.3+
 - FAME.library 4.0+
 - DRE.library 1.2+
@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
 
 @{b}INTRODUCTION@{ub}

 @{b}Product Info:@{ub}

     @{b}Features:@{ub}
 
 dRE!WhO is a very powerfull and free configable who and frontend door
 in one file...
 Have a look at the features...
 
 - unlimited styles (public version is limited to have 2)
 + preferences editor to save the choosen style
 +  Argument parsing - you can use WHO 2 to view style #2
 + totally free configuring of the stlyes via config-files
 + supports 100% hidden mode
 + own identify how to run as who or as frontend door
 - supports monitor mode
 - supports the FORCE mode
 
 + and even some more fine options

 @{b}All options marked with '-' are only for registered Users!
 @{ub}
 @{b}@{u}NOTE:@{ub}@{uu} Some features are disabled in the public version
@endnode

